 any recent news?\u201d Abu Musa said, \u201cYes, a man turned back to unbelief\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3389,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/06\/16\/work-rizq-like-birds\/","url_meta":{"origin":20698,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Reliance: Must work for provision like the birds","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 16, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Umar ibn al-Khattab reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf you were to rely upon Allah with reliance due to Him, He would provide for you just as He provides for the birds. They go out in the morning with empty stomachs and return\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5865,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/03\/umar-moderation-love-hatred\/","url_meta":{"origin":20698,"position":5},"title":"Umar on Moderation: Be moderate in your love and hatred","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 3, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aslam reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cLet not your love be infatuation and let not your hatred be destruction.\u201d It was said, \u201cHow is this?\u201d Umar said, \u201cWhen you love someone, you become infatuated like a child. When you hate someone, you love destruction\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621